{"tid":212221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Gobee.bike首個周末兩單車遭丟城門河創辦人嘆未料香港竟發生","createTime":"2017-04-22T09:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T12:47:36.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8797cdcaf9cd48c02d14e0f74c53f40670a4e1d3","tid":212221,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/86095?utm_content=buffereecb1&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F86095%3Futm_content%3Dbuffereecb1%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=641b3389\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/86095?utm_content=buffereecb1&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\n全港首個智能單車共享服務推出不夠一星期，不料首個周末已經「出事」！今日下午，Gobee.Bike發現其中兩輛單車被棄置於城門河，投入運作後首個周末已經「遭殃」。禍不單行，Gobee.Bike早上被揭發有保安漏洞，用戶的信用卡資料有機會外洩。<br />\nGobeeBike城巿策劃經理李淑澄表示，下午接獲警方通知，指在城門河近體院附近發現有兩輛單車被棄置。GobeeBike現正派人到場了解事件。她又表示，早前已有部分的單車遭到惡意破壞。李淑澄又指，早前已有用家發現，部分單車的手柄零件懷疑遭到惡意破壞，亦有零件被人偷去。創辦人Raphael Cohen慨嘆，料不到香港竟會出現這種情況。<br />\n<br />\n立法會交通事務委員會委員、公民黨議員楊岳橋對事件表示可惜，認為GobeeBike是新嘗試，香港人整體而言願意接受新事物，「不覺得一件事就證明香港人點樣點樣」。他希望Gobee Bike在配件及網絡安全方面再作提升，「日後大家一齊進步」。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人說，於下午2時37分接獲一名男子報案，指在沙田路近錦龍橋發現三架單車被丟入河邊，警方列作求警調查處理。"},{"pid":"9971acd94da85593487f6af6859bc0aeb6d7f1b4","tid":212221,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"畀行家搞，一貫x社會造法黎啦。"},{"pid":"ce0a7d493de0b8d63d7d7a2082bb7fc1250b6d2d","tid":212221,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"香港+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eb6535a27c656d183e54c41deb9ff30241b5a6","tid":212221,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f805182e90f4b2ac371be3507ab36f51c46b2fd2","tid":212221,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:13:17.000Z","msg":"香港做生意同行家鬥既黑暗面"},{"pid":"94753f04388ff56690360358c689b13ba8ee2232","tid":212221,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}